<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for choosing Kingsbridge for your business insurance.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>I tried to call you today to make sure you have received all of your insurance documents and to answer any questions you may have about the policy.<br></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b>Your feedback is very important to us and we would like to hear about your experience when purchasing your insurance. Our independent review service, Feefo, will be in touch via email asking you to provide feedback.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please don't hesitate to get in touch on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> 740 if you have any queries.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
